This one is for every single loyal RCB fan who stood by the team no matter what! Who were genuine towards only the team’s victory and never to bring another team down. Who took the trolls seamlessly and found a way to smile through it. Who longed patiently, holding on to the team no matter how many years it took! You guys are crazy! Congrats on the well-deserved win!!!

And today finally marks the day to be etched in history forever! RCB lifts the trophy after 18 years of constant hustle! This victory is truly deserving for the entire team and of course, for our most beloved KING! As we got to see him all teared up, each one of us could literally feel it at that moment!

Happy for RCB and for my man as he got to see his KING happy! ❤️ 

-From a CSK fangirl.
